t: Nyang leupah musoh keu ureueng mukmin Keubit takalon Yahudi jadah Sabe ngon muchrek kaphe harbi Awak Yahudi hana meuubah Teuma takalon nyang laen lagi Awak Nasrani droejih jipeugah Di jih leubeh toe ngon ureueng mukmin Silatur rahim han that meupisah Sabab na raheb dalam kawan jih í Pendeta di jih pih na jikeubah (QUZ 7) Awaknyan teuma hana teukabo d Han that jitajo bak buet nyang salah